<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Evergreen Media started.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Evergreen Media started.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Salomon Brothers said it started coverage of Evergreen Media Corp with a buy rating.</p>
<p>-- Estimates earnings at loss $1.43 per share in 1997, loss $1.86 per share in 1998 and loss $1.11 per share in 1999.</p>
<p>-- Estimates after-tax cash flow at $2.25 per share in 1997, $2.85 per share in 1998 and $3.75 per share in 1999.</p>
<p>-- Set 12-18 month target price at $45 per share.</p>
<p>-- Shares rose 1/4 to 32-5/8.</p>
<p>((-- Wall Street desk, 212-859-1730))</p>
